<p><strong>Part 3 (Writing)</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Question:</strong> Write a short email to a friend, inviting them to a party.</li>
<li><strong>Answer:</strong> Dear [Friend's Name], I hope this email finds you well. I'm writing to invite you to a party I'm having on [Date] at [Time] at my house. I'm really excited to celebrate with you and some of our other friends. Please let me know if you can make it. Best regards, [Your Name].</li>
</ul>
